# node-pytpl-bin 

[pytpl](http://pytpl.sourceforge.net) 0.1.0 Node.js wrapper that makes pytpl template engine seamlessly available as a local dependency.

> pytpl is python template engine.

## Install

Install with [npm](https://npmjs.org/package/pytpl-bin): `npm install --save pytpl-bin`


## Example usage

```js
var execFile = require('child_process').execFile;
var pytplPath = require('pytpl-bin').path;

execFile(pytplPath, ['-v'], function(err, stdout, stderr) {
    console.log('pytpl running');
});
```

Can also be run directly from `./node_modules/.bin/pytpl`.


